  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.4.3">
<l>paṭalaṭaitta ciṟukurampai nuḻaintu pukkup pacuveṇṇey patamārap paṇṇai muṟṟum</l>
<l>aṭalaṭartta vēṟkaṇṇār tōkkai paṟṟi yalantalaimai ceytuḻalu maiyaṉ kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>maṭaleṭutta neṭuṉteṅkiṉ paḻaṅkaḷ vīḻa māṅkaṉikaḷ tiraṭṭuruṭṭā varunīrp poṉṉi</l>
<l>tiṭaleṭuttu malarcumantaṅ kiḻiyu nāṅkūrt tirutteṟṟi yampalatteṉ ceṅkaṇ mālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The gentleman who wanders the women’s quarters, making trouble,</l>
<l rend="indent">snatching at the clothes	 of those with eyes [like] spears</l>
<l rend="indent">which attack in battle,</l>
<l>And entering, creeping, into little huts with leaf doors shut</l>
<l rend="indent">to eat dairy butter, you see,</l>
<l>Is my bright-eyed Māl in Tirutteṟṟiyampalam in Nāṅkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where the Poṉṉi descends, burdened with blossoms</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] carrying off hummocks,</l>
<l>The waters moving while rolling clusters of mangoes,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the fruit of tall coconut [palms] fall which takes [off its] fronds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
